1. run shell as root
sudo -i

2. generate pub key for github
ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -m pem

3. get key context
cat .ssh/id_rsa.pub

4. add key to github
https://github.com/settings/keys

5. clone repo
git clone https://github.com/ArgLuna/Ubuntu_scripts

6. set the following fields in init.conf.sh if required. they are not set by default.
USER
for disable sudo password.

HOSTNAME
change hostname.

7. run run.sh
